data.description: ** OPEN HOUSE 11am-2pm Saturday 2/3 AND Sunday 2/4** This GORGEOUS one-story home is immaculate and move-in ready! Nestled in a peaceful community, this GEM features an open floor plan with high ceilings and tons of natural light! Beautiful kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, cabinets with ENORMOUS amounts of storage, ample counter space with an island breakfast-bar adjacent to the dining area; this kitchen is the heart of the home. Impressive primary suite highlights a huge walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom complete with dual sinks and separate tub/shower. Large flex room offers an extra living space that can be used as an office, playroom, game room, gym or anything you desire! The backyard is perfect for all your outdoor activities and offers a covered patio for relaxing and entertaining! This home has many post-construction upgrades to include custom barn door to the guest suite, upgraded lighting, water softener, garage shelving, and an extended backyard patio!! Builder upgrades include extended home office/4th bedroom/flex room, bay windows in master suite, 50' oversized lot, 11' vaulted ceilings and double-door entry to master bath!! Great curb appeal with landscaping and sprinkler system. This home is part of the master planned community of Cinco Lakes with amenities to include a large swimming pool, clubhouse cabana, and a park with playscape. Quick 10m drive to the Shops at Dove Creek, Costco, and HEB Plus! Close proximity to major highways, 1604, Hwy 90, UT Health Science Center, Southwest Research Institute, Toyota Manufacturing, Port San Antonio, USAA, and 15 minutes to Lackland AFB!! You will LOVE this home. Schedule your showing today!
